  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "勒波德 Mark 4 HAMR 4x24 DeltaPoint混合式突击瞄准镜",
      "en": "Leupold Mark 4 HAMR 4x24 DeltaPoint hybrid assault scope"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "HAMR",
      "en": "HAMR"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "这款由Leupold生产的混合式瞄准镜包含Mark 4 HAMR 4x24毫米光学瞄准镜和安装于上方的DeltaPoint反射式瞄准镜。这种瞄准镜可通过4倍光学瞄准镜提供精准的中距离瞄准，并在必要时通过更紧凑的反射式瞄准镜提供更有效的近距离瞄准。",
      "en": "The Hybrid Leupold-produced scope comprises of the Mark 4 HAMR 4x24mm optical sight with the DeltaPoint reflex sight installed on top of it. It was developed for precision mid-range carbine fire using the 4x optics while being equally effective in close quarters thanks to use of compact reflex sight when necessary."
    },
